            <!-- Editions, Translations, and Relevant Publications -->
            <noteGrp type="publications">
               <note type="editions">A critical edition of the Arabic text and a commentary in
                     German was first produced H S Nyberg’s Kleinere Schriften des Ibn al-ʿArabî,
                     (Leiden 1919), pp. 1-38. The Arabic text was reproduced in Fenton and Gloton’s
                     French translation La Productions des cercles (Paris, 1996). Critical edition
                     by Maurizio Marconi in Azufre Rojo vol. 5 (2018). A new critical edition, plus
                     a translation into Urdu, is forthcoming from the Ibn ʿArabī Foundation
                     (Rawalpindi, Pakistan). Ed. Abrār Aḥmad Shāhī, not yet published.</note>
               <note type="translations">English translation by Paul Fenton and Maurice Gloton:
                     ‘The Book of the Description of the Encompassing Circles’ in Muhyiddin Ibn
                     ʿArabī (1165-1240), London, 1993 French translation by Paul Fenton and Maurice
                     Gloton: La Productions des cercles, Paris, 1996. Italian translation by
                     Maurizio Marconi: ‘Il Libro della produzione dei cerchi (kitâb
                     inshâ’i-d-dawâ’ir)’, publication forthcoming (probably 2015).</note>
